<!-- SOLUTION -->
<div class="page" id="page-solution">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="eyebrow">The Solution</div>
    <h2 class="headline">iBita — The All-in-One Healthcare Communication Platform</h2>
    <p class="lead">A multilingual mobile and web app creating a 24/7 direct bridge between patients and providers — replacing four to six separate vendor subscriptions with one seamless platform.</p>
    <div class="g3">
      <div class="card card-left"><div class="c-icon">&#128193;</div><div class="c-title">Structured Survey Flow</div><p class="c-body">6-step guided complaint submission routes directly to the correct department — billing, personnel, or healthcare — with structured patient data, never free text lost in a phone system.</p></div>
      <div class="card card-left"><div class="c-icon">&#127908;</div><div class="c-title">Voice and Text Messaging</div><p class="c-body">Record a voice note or type your concern. Audio is transmitted securely alongside full structured report data to the appropriate supervisor in real time, 24/7.</p></div>
      <div class="card card-left"><div class="c-icon">&#128100;</div><div class="c-title">Anonymous Reporting</div><p class="c-body">Staff and patients can submit full reports with zero identity collection — eliminating fear of retaliation and enabling the honest, complete feedback that providers need to improve.</p></div>
